On this podcast I sit down with my friend Arial Messerli and talk to her about her experience through the pandemic. I think her perspective is very interesting because she is in a new relationship&nbsp;and also living with her partner. She talks about some of the activities she planned to spice things up, and how they got stronger during the pandemic.
